{"tid":1809947,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"美國禁售部分口味電子煙","createTime":"2020-01-03T12:40:33.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-03T12:45:08.000Z","uid":51469,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"7705fa6edafccbd8b7c715aca9e2565441fa2c1e","tid":1809947,"uid":51469,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-03T12:40:33.000Z","msg":"【Now新聞台】美國禁止出售部分口味的電子煙，希望遏止青少年使用電子煙。<br />\n<br />\n美國食品及藥物管理局將會禁止水果、糖果、薄荷及甜品味的電子煙，但煙草味和薄荷醇味就獲得豁免，同時不會限制與裝置分開出售的電子煙油，禁令將在30日後生效，此後如有公司繼續生產、分銷或出售被禁的電子煙產品，將面臨制裁。<br />\n<br />\n根據現行法例，管理局容許部分有助成人戒煙的電子煙產品在市面出售，當局會在五月開始檢查所有電子煙產品，產品要對美國公共衛生有利才可留在市面。<br />\n<br />\n聯邦調查顯示美國目前有兩成七高中生吸食電子煙，有組織批評禁令豁免薄荷醇味電子煙，令青少年仍有上癮的風險，只有禁止所有加味電子煙，才能令電子煙在青少年當中不再流行。<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.now.com/home/international/player?newsId=375427\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fhome%2Finternational%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D375427&d=GDp31xM3xvXFOTrKf8Ol7FBOXtrJgaeu%2B3uDm9UxZFo%3D&h=7546ad28\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fhome%2Finternational%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D375427&h=d71c92f4\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.now.com/home/international/player?newsId=375427</a>"},{"pid":"e96efee6d5ddbc7da7730fba2821a27ae9e4c8a5","tid":1809947,"uid":159448,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-03T12:42:16.000Z","msg":"烏龍茶味好食<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/wine.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a62e30ecd776e1db4b24de8c089fe34164a43863","tid":1809947,"uid":292710,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"e96efee6d5ddbc7da7730fba2821a27ae9e4c8a5","tid":1809947,"uid":159448,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-03T12:42:16.000Z","msg":"烏龍茶味好食<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/wine.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-03T12:44:29.000Z","msg":"2020香港普選聯署：<br />\n<a href=\"https://petitions.whitehouse.gov/petition/hong-kong-universal-suffrage-plan\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=ht